                <h1>Gun Control: Balancing Safety and Rights</h1>
                <p>Gun control is a critical issue that sparks intense debate. Advocates argue for stricter laws to enhance public safety and reduce gun violence, emphasizing the need for background checks and restrictions on certain firearms. Opponents claim that such measures infringe upon Second Amendment rights. Finding a balance remains a challenge for lawmakers.</p>
